You can simply ask Alexa to turn the light on, off, or dim. There's no need to go to the switch to adjust the light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
To connect Alexa to your Qualitronix products, please follow a few simple steps:
(1). Download our QualiHome app from the Android or iOS app stores;
(2). Register a user in the QualiHome application;
(3). You need to have some Qualitronix smart devices on hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our QualiHome app and choose the appropriate name for your devices that will be used in Skill QualiHome;
(5). Download the Alexa app on Android, iOS or the Amazon app store;
(6). Configure the Echo with the Alexa app;
(7). Search Skill QualiHome from the Skills category of the Alexa app;
(8). Enable Skill QualiHome;
(9). Now that all setup is complete. You can enjoy voice control on your home devices like these: 
-Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.
-Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.
-Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.
-Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.
-Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%.
-Alexa, set bedroom light to green.
-Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white.
